                    "description": "<div style='font-family: sans-serif; color: #334155; background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;'><p style='margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6;'>This project solves the \"data desynchronization\" problem of having a CV outdated relative to the web portfolio. I treated professional experience as a master dataset, creating a decoupled architecture for real-time content management and on-demand \"pixel-perfect\" PDF generation.</p><div style='background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; margin-top: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);'><h3 style='color: #0f172a; margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9; padding-bottom: 10px;'>Engineering Solution</h3><p style='margin-bottom: 0;'>Designed a <strong>Decoupled Full-Stack</strong> architecture where the backend acts as the Single Source of Truth. Implemented a high-performance cache layer with <strong>Redis</strong> for sub-millisecond response times, and a server-side rendering engine (WeasyPrint) that transforms structured JSON data into professional PDFs on the fly.</p></div><div style='background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; margin-top: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);'><h3 style='color: #0f172a; margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9; padding-bottom: 10px;'>System Capabilities</h3><ul style='margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 20px;'><li><strong>Headless Content Management:</strong> Secure admin panel (OAuth) to update projects without redeploying code.</li><li><strong>Document Generation Pipeline:</strong> Automated engine assembling the CV in real-time based on the latest DB data.</li><li><strong>Performance Optimization:</strong> Hybrid cache strategy (Memory + Redis) reducing PostgreSQL load by 95%.</li></ul></div><h3 style='margin-top: 24px; color: #0f172a;'>Operational Impac